data.description: This one of a kind home has all the charm & comfort you would expect from a timeless, turn of the century build! The warmth and craftsmanship are a rare find. Matching the historic charm, you can benefit from the wonderful modern updates throughout, such as a new roof, furnace, hot tub pump and many more. Setting foot onto the property, you will be impressed by the mature landscaping that offers beauty and privacy. The living space offers a cozy fireplace, wonderful natural light and large wrap around window seating, perfect for gatherings. The formal dining area is perfectly situated off the living area and kitchen, creating a nice flow to the home. The owner's bedroom is on the main level and features a half bath and a private patio that leads to the hot tub (enclosed spa room). The kitchen is full of charm and leads to the back patio which is a lush oasis. Come experience all this property has to offer.
